// Per-developer local overrides.
//
// Copy this file to `Local.xcconfig` in the same folder — that copy is
// git-ignored, so your personal values are never committed. The Debug and
// Release xcconfigs pull it in via `#include? "Local.xcconfig"`.
//
// Set your Apple Developer Team ID so device builds can be signed:
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM=YOUR_TEAM_ID
